dBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:17:38.000Z","msg":"開始向下了"},{"pid":"b5c164f6b0e8d638f41efd85f5aa860d0859bab2","tid":2460124,"uid":377375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:18:57.000Z","msg":"今日勁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4982e9cd3dc7551a306ed8c625a082be9b4f18bd","tid":2460124,"uid":262746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:31:20.000Z","msg":"其實長渣tsm，soxl，半導電體股點會輸<br />\n咩科技都要半導電，需求愈來愈大<br />\n生意多到做唔晒<br />\n除左18大市跌，年年ytd都大升<br />\n直接all in 唔洗煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe0d5ca88c530e72a4df7eec58b977f153de8c5","tid":2460124,"uid":346744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa74b13c9ba8508e35a5ac4cc8be96e692005678","tid":2460124,"uid":346744,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T15:55:34.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"orange\"><strong>持有策略，愈跌愈買愈安心</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n基於資本配置和股價驅動力的不一樣，投資人持有台積電的策略、態度和方向，也必須不一樣。<br />\n<br />\n面對台積電，要學會看懂一家一流企業未來的成長性，要有長期的視野。你應該放鬆心情去享受波動，同時把時間用在經營別的地方，甚至可以創個副業，賺的錢再丟給台積電。如果花太多時間在意台積電的波動，我覺得你失去了那份優雅，也失去和一流企業共同成長的感覺。若一直在玩短線的波動，在那邊浮浮沉沉，可能賺了錢，卻丟了心情，我覺得沒有必要。<br />\n<br />\n台積電這檔股票，是屬於擁有它，而不是去交易它的一種「存股」概念。你不要把太多的心思用於「在存股當中做價差」，要做價差有其它股票可利用，但台積電是「跌下馬背，要趕快上馬」。我要引申的是，台積電是一旦跌了，但你不會怕的股票，這是很多股票做不到的。<br />\n<br />\n彼得．林區曾說過，「買進一檔股票下跌了，不代表你買錯；上漲了，也不代表你買對。」台積電就是買進後萬一下跌，也不代表買錯的股票。下跌時投資人不需要驚慌，而且要感到高興，因為就算它跌了20%至30%，若未來可以翻倍成長，這時候，跌20%、30% 會那麼困擾你嗎？未來五年內，台積電是「愈跌、愈買、會愈安心」的股票，這個特質是其他股票不具備的。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.moneyweekly.com.tw/ArticleData/Info/%E8%AA%AA%E8%A7%A3%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/51920/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneyweekly.com.tw%2FArticleData%2FInfo%2F%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BA%258B%2F51920%2F&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2Fxom5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=ddf06354\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.moneyweekly.com.tw/ArticleData/Info/%E8%AA%AA%E8%A7%A3%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/51920/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:40:25.000Z","msg":"準備每日bin屍 負評我果班傻閪"},{"pid":"b49726d30eab908082bfd6f22e1d7018ef5d7b47","tid":2460124,"uid":28645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4982e9cd3dc7551a306ed8c625a082be9b4f18bd","tid":2460124,"uid":262746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:31:20.000Z","msg":"其實長渣tsm，soxl，半導電體股點會輸<br />\n咩科技都要半導電，需求愈來愈大<br />\n生意多到做唔晒<br />\n除左18大市跌，年年ytd都大升<br />\n直接all in 唔洗煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:45:57.000Z","msg":"Soxl 得閒仲可以行出行入玩下波波<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab77445346db78430e295f8dd60d419ba1c7b8fc","tid":2460124,"uid":18547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:52:41.000Z","msg":"硬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56af0ae8cdb98be06befe8003e9a6ce3481346a6","tid":2460124,"uid":18547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e805d7cbfada49de3cfdd5af33957e6003a36dbb","tid":2460124,"uid":100772,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T15:31:59.000Z","msg":"日日係咁跌 你地就日日話幾勁幾勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:54:18.000Z","msg":"之前依到仲有條柒頭鬧我屌台積電廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a050d52a6c96782f1c956ec56f91923a6437c62b","tid":2460124,"uid":313692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T17:18:06.000Z","msg":"每月加少少算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif